title: Leaverbuster warning "ok" doesn't work

embed.description: Yes I also tried to add a dot at the end LOL

body: Video link is up so things are easier to explain. I tried everything you can possibly think of and it still wouldn't work.

replies.body:
This **may** be a very dumb question but did you try typing it both words capitalized without quotes?

>I Agree

Like that?
Yes, I tried "i agree" / "I agree" / "I Agree" / "I agree." and none of those worked.

You need to type exactly what the blue text is showing you. No quotations, both first letters capitalized. 

I Agree

I think you should even be able to copy paste that ^
Just wanted to make sure since I didn't see it in teh video :)
